title: Dayton's /Walker Gallery: Frank Stella
medium: White kraft paper with electron beam coating; tinted twisted paper handle.
description: Reproduction of aspects of a Frank Stella painting: red, yellow, green and purple intersecting lines; yellow background with red rectangle. Side panels: Facsimile signature: F. Stella, '84. Text in red, black, green gray: Dayton's salutes the opening of the Walker Art Center's new galleries. Premiere exhibition selections from Tyler Graphics, 23 September 1984 - March 1985.
name: Shopping bag
